<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dream-n">dream <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /driːm/    美 /driːm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 梦；睡梦：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>had</strong> a bad <strong>dream</strong> last night. 
昨晚我做了一个噩梦。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 梦想；理想；愿望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>realize one’s dream</strong>
实现某人的梦想</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a “dream team” 
梦之队</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Chris was delighted when his dream came true.
当梦想成真的时候克里斯非常高兴。</p><footer>2013 安徽改</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>梦一般美妙的人 / 事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That meal was an absolute dream. 
那顿饭真是太棒了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My uncle says that he never dreams becoming rich in a short period of time.  （2016 全国 改错）  </li>
<li>Owning a house of their own is a <strong><em>_</em></strong> (梦想) for the young couple.   （2009 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. dreams 后加 of  2. dream  </p></div>